New Records: Patrick Yazbek earns a recall for the first time since his international debut against Lebanon in March 2024.
Luke Brattan joins the Subway Socceroos’ squad for the first time since 2018.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Tickets for the match start from $15 Child, $20 Concession, $29 Adult, and $58 Family via Ticketek.
Others: The match is part of the AFC Asian Qualifiers™ – Road to 26, which features three groups of six teams playing in a home-and-away, round-robin format, offering direct qualification to the FIFA World Cup 2026™ for the top two finishers of each group.
